//www.cracked.com/article_26965_a-third-kevin-spacey-accuser-died-which-seems-like-lot.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cracked.com%2Farticle_26965_a-third-kevin-spacey-accuser-died-which-seems-like-lot.html&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=d99a5f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cracked.com/article_26965_a-third-kevin-spacey-accuser-died-which-seems-like-lot.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"如果你有跟，係有個事主唔肯做證。<br />\n幾單係1986, 2003, 2008, 2010, 2012 直到佢收貔之後呢 D 受害人一係 Drop Charge 一係死咗。<br />\n咁多單都入唔到，佢無同任何人做過 Settlement 佢亦都無黑幫記錄。<br />\n咁到底佢係因為 Gay 被誣告，定係佢可以洗黑手殺咗三個人嚇怕其他人呢？後者我諗難 D。"},{"pid":"4b5ebd37b4bc659ec87832b3731f3c46b972decc","tid":1814503,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}